			</imageobject>
		</mediaobject>
	

	 Use the following id for the parameter
		"de.vogella.rcp.commands.parameterfirst.commandParameter1"

	
image::parameter20.gif" />
				
			</imageobject>
		</mediaobject>
	

	In the handler you have to evaluate the parameter.

	
		<programlisting>
